reviewText:
Never used to believe......UNTIL I SAW THIS DVD....YOU WAN'T PROOF...HERE IT IS!!!!!!!

Should be on news!!!!!

Produced in the grand tradition of "Alien Autopsy" and "Conspiracy Theory".  The SOLE purpose of this production is to get you to part with your money via the ploy of sensationalistic claims.  If you believe everything you read in the supermarket tabloids, then by all means, go for it.
I want to know much as much as possible about U.F.O
